result.title: When did Watermelon overtake Theater Square?
result.content: For the past few months I've been anticipating Watermelon to pass Theater Square in number of solves. During this period, number of Theater square solves has been ahead of Watermelon, fluctuating between something like 20 â€” 150 solves. I haven't checked in about a week, but suddenly today Watermelon is ahead by 120!! So does anyone know the exact moment this happened? (Also woo it finally happened!)
